OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSedition law: India's      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FSupreme Court puts         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcontroversial law on hold  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's Supreme Court has put a        
OL,6, controversial colonial-era sedition law
OL,7, on hold that critics say is used to    
OL,8, stifle dissent.                        
OL,10,FThe judges asked the government to     
OL,11,Frefrain from registering any new cases 
OL,12,Fwhich invoke sedition until it finishes
OL,13,Fhearing petitions challenging it.      
OL,15,FThe court also asked the authorities to
OL,16,Fpause all existing sedition trials.    
OL,18,FThe government has been accused of     
OL,19,Fusing the law against critics, such as 
OL,20,Fpoliticians, journalists and activists.
